合.meaning: (formal) meeting with a view to marriage

当.meaning: being in charge (of an area of responsibility)

開.meaning: opening (of a new road, railway, etc.)

持.meaning: to be able to possess (hold, get, etc.)

住.meaning: (level of) comfort (in the place one lives)

夕.meaning: (sudden, heavy) shower (on a summer afternoon or evening)

低.meaning: low (rank, degree, value, content, quality, etc.)

服.meaning: conquest (of a difficulty, illness, crisis, etc.)

質.meaning: quality (of a product or a service)

鳥.meaning: killing two birds with one stone

特.meaning: limited express (train for which a limited-express ticket is required)

未.meaning: failed attempt (at a crime, suicide, etc.)

束.meaning: to tie up in a bundle (e.g. straw, hair, bills, letters)

台.meaning: stage (of a theatre, concert hall, etc.)
